===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''isomer'''
#{{chemistry}} Any of two or more [[compound]]s with the same [[molecular formula]] but with different [[structure]].
#{{physics}} Any of two or more [[nuclei]] with the ame [[mass number]] and [[atomic number]] but with different [[radioactive]] properties.
